Wortschatz,trans,Vocabulary,is,a,collection,of,German,language,linguistics,services,hosted,by,Leipzig,University,These,services,provide,extensive,information,pertaining,to,individual,words,such,as,the,lemmatized,base,form,of,the,word,sample,sentences,using,the,word,usage,frequency,synonyms,contextually,similar,words,and,co,occurrences,with,other,words,Wortschatz,also,provides,services,for,working,with,word,patterns,and,n,grams,These,functions,are,all,accessible,using,the,Wortschatz,SOAP,APIs,The,Wortschatz,website,and,API,documentation,are,given,in,German